### CCR-017 §1 — EventFlightStatus enum 공유
###
### 검증:
### - Flight status가 정수 enum (0~6, 3 skip)
### - is_registerable, day_index, is_pause 필드 반영
### - is_restricted = (status==1 && day_index>=1) 판정

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}

### 60.1 GET /api/v1/events/1/flights — 목록 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/events/1/flights
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK
# {
#   "flights": [
#     {
#       "id": "fl_01HVQK...",
#       "event_id": "ev_...",
#       "display_name": "Day 1A",
#       "status": 1,                    // 정수 enum (Announce)
#       "status_label": "Announce",     // UI 표시용
#       "is_registerable": true,
#       "day_index": 0,
#       "is_pause": false
#     },
#     {
#       "display_name": "Day 2",
#       "status": 1,                    // Announce
#       "day_index": 1,
#       "is_registerable": true
#       // is_restricted = true (status==Announce && day_index>=1)
#     }
#   ]
# }

### 60.2 PATCH /api/v1/flights/{id} — status 전이 (Announce → Running)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/flights/fl_01HVQK-day1a
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "status": 4
}

# Announce(1) → Running(4): 정상 전이
# 3 skip이므로 2 → 4는 허용
# 예상: 200 OK

### 60.3 PATCH — 역방향 전이 (Running → Announce)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/flights/fl_01HVQK-day1a
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "status": 1
}

# 예상: 422 Unprocessable Entity
# { "error": "INVALID_STATUS_TRANSITION", "from": 4, "to": 1 }

### 60.4 PATCH — status == 3 (skip 값)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/flights/fl_01HVQK-day1a
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "status": 3
}

# 예상: 422 Unprocessable Entity
# { "error": "INVALID_STATUS_VALUE", "value": 3, "valid": [0,1,2,4,5,6] }

### 60.5 PATCH — is_pause toggle (Late Reg 타이머 stop)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/flights/fl_01HVQK-day1a
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "is_pause": true
}

# 예상: 200 OK
# 부수효과: Late Reg 남은 시간 계산에서 elapsed_in_current_level 증가 중단

### 60.6 GET /api/v1/flights/{id}/late-reg-remaining — pause 동작 확인
GET {{host}}/api/v1/flights/fl_01HVQK-day1a/late-reg-remaining
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK
# {
#   "late_reg_remaining_seconds": 1800,
#   "is_pause": true,
#   "last_tick_at": "2026-04-10T14:30:00Z"  // pause 시작 시각
# }
#
# pause 해제 후 재조회 시 last_tick_at 이후 경과한 초가 차감됨

### 60.7 마이그레이션 검증 — 기존 문자열 status → 정수 enum
###
### 수동 SQL 검증:
### SELECT id, display_name, status FROM flights;
### - 모든 status 값이 INTEGER 타입
### - NULL 없음
### - 'active' → 4, 'pending' → 1 or 0, 'done' → 5 로 변환됐는지
